Package: moexer
Type: Package
Title: Interact with Moscow Exchange Informational and Statistical Server ('ISS')
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dmitry Zotikov <dmitry.zotikov@ungrund.org>
Maintainer: Dmitry Zotikov <dmitry.zotikov@ungrund.org>
Description: This is a thin wrapper around the 'MOEX' 'ISS' REST interface.  
    It allows to quickly fetch price candles for a particular security, obtain 
    its profile information and so on.
